[{'title': 'E-Commerce ', 'date': {'start': {'month': 9, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 12, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}}, 'description': 'The concept consists of a group of students creating an e-commerce concept for the product of their choice.

', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Anja', 'last_name': 'Konjević', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Employer Branding and Social Media at DHL Global Forwarding'}]}, {'title': 'Qualitative Research ', 'date': {'start': {'month': 9, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 12, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}}, 'description': "The concept of the project consists of developing qualitative research based on the topic of students' choice. 
I have chosen to interview five Croatian students who have experienced a gap year. The purpose of the research was to discover misconceptions that the population has about taking a gap year, but also to present the advantages and disadvantages of taking a gap year.  ", 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Anja', 'last_name': 'Konjević', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Employer Branding and Social Media at DHL Global Forwarding'}]}, {'title': 'Design Thinking ', 'date': {'start': {'month': 2, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}}, 'description': 'The concept of the project consists of a group of students developing a prototype of the sustainable product and creating the marketing campaign for that product. 
The group I have worked in was focused on creating a 100% sustainable denim bag that can be used for different purposes. By the end of the project, we created the prototype, official website, and the whole social media campaign. ', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Anja', 'last_name': 'Konjević', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Employer Branding and Social Media at DHL Global Forwarding'}]}, {'title': 'Online Marketing ', 'date': {'start': {'month': 2, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}}, 'description': 'The concept of the project consists of a group of students optimizing the online appearance of the company Dailydream. 
During the time of the projects, I have gained a certain knowledge in the topics of SEA, SEO, and display advertising. 
By the end of the project, we have developed the website with the online shop, recommendations for the marketing campaign, and financial projection. ', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Anja', 'last_name': 'Konjević', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Employer Branding and Social Media at DHL Global Forwarding'}]}, {'title': 'Quantitative Research ', 'date': {'start': {'month': 2, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}}, 'description': 'The concept of the project consists of a group of students developing and executing quantitative marketing research. 
The group I have worked in was interested in how brand Milka can improve its performance in the Dutch market. We were able to discover possible reasons for the certain brand loyalty of the customers and the current trends that can influence the purchasing. Based on the answers to the survey that we have distributed, we were able to give recommendations. ', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Anja', 'last_name': 'Konjević', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Employer Branding and Social Media at DHL Global Forwarding'}]}, {'title': 'Desk Research ', 'date': {'start': {'month': 9, 'day': None, 'year': 2019}, 'end': {'month': 12, 'day': None, 'year': 2019}}, 'description': 'The concept of the project consists of analyzing the macro-business environment and researching how a business or industry can be affected by it.
